{"tid":364382,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［molamola]Gem牛一戰鬥格 男友買Cheap酒上家過夜","createTime":"2017-08-18T10:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T06:47:29.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40d8ca0c508e170c1f5b7d9875b24d5ed452ea64","tid":364382,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/184430_57d2143247d9692b1ec97fe64cc6fad5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F184430_57d2143247d9692b1ec97fe64cc6fad5.jpg&h=77a043ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20170818/540557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20170818%2F540557&d=2vDNIUYz5qXsf6EDuQG7r0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8b46c3b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fent%2F20170818%2F540557&h=06909022\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/ent/20170818/540557</a><br />\n <br />\n一副戰鬥格的阿Gem同男朋友阿Mark，一齊到半島行慶祝阿Gem 26歲生日。阿Mark還很花心思買了盒64支玫瑰送給女朋友，埋單都要成二千一百蚊，氹到阿Gem即時擺上網。看她的Hastag，阿Gem應該恨收花恨了很久了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拍拖第一次慶祝燭光晚餐少不得，去半島酒店當然要著得靚一點，短裙仔是常識吧。食完阿Mark同阿Gem去取車，不過阿Gem這個眼神有暗示。之後二人上車直回阿Gem家，難得今晚同女朋友過二人世界，阿Mark就買了支紅酒上去，這支酒100元有找，認真便宜。<br />\n<br />\n阿Mark之後急急腳去找阿Gem上樓，撞正兩個大燈泡站著，因為fans知偶像生日，當然要過來送禮物。等fans走了之後，阿Mark已經急不及待等阿Gem落車，話明是超超超短裙，一對大髀一覽無遺，就算走光也不怕，都是只有阿Mark看而已。<br />\n《壹》仔等了2個多小時，阿Mark都沒有下來，春宵一刻值千金，生日都係要放肆下。"},{"pid":"1eede0aaa44f42f263de38627008de3a13452272","tid":364382,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"阿槳隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成晚係咁扑，肯定嗌得拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74863ae4c76fd2398446f7e2898da2d0e06056e1","tid":364382,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"成個胡紅釣咁"},{"pid":"88d0a56f35173bed8de172fca2dff5719c518f71","tid":364382,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b17601240c2e68becdfd67ee2c991d8fd54a3d0","tid":364382,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"條裙咁短<br />\n會唔會一入屋就俾條仔瘋狂奶閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c738f39775e9ddc41bf3ab9835c29a8ddca2077c","tid":364382,"uid":137924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:03:00.000Z","msg":"molamola"},{"pid":"19173bd46bd16ffbbd4b6609195df2333b720ac8","tid":364382,"uid":29675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:07:09.000Z","msg":"兒夜姨野以夜儀野"},{"pid":"2603c4dc53e42a3d7f7cc1e75a2bef1879678a5c","tid":364382,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"佢N年前都mola"},{"pid":"169c7f243a23e5ab63a03f02886b6205a4a24687","tid":364382,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"那個了哦"},{"pid":"2589ac8496416943d0caff6f4d3106a9c86879b1